Package: dash
Type: Package
Title: Dirichlet Adaptive Shrinkage (dash) of Compositional data 
Version: 0.99.0
Author: c(
    person("Kushal", "Dey", email = "kkdey@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Matthew", "Stephens", email = "mstephens@uchicago.edu", role = c("ctb")))
Maintainer: Kushal K. Dey <kkdey@uchicago.edu>
Description: Performs adaptive shrinkage of compositional counts data using Dirichlet adaptive shrinkage (dash). the package fits a multinomial counts data with a mixture prior of Dirichlet components of varying concentrations (ranging from very high to very low) to adaptively shrink the compositional probabilities. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), SQUAREM, LaplacesDemon
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/kkdey/dash
LazyData: true
Imports: SQUAREM, LaplacesDemon
Suggests: ashr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
